ntation is memory-based. We also found cells that encoded the distance to the goal, often in conjunction with goal direction. The goal-direction and goal-distance signals make up a vectorial representation of spatial goals, suggesting a previously unrecognized neuronal mechanism for goal-directed navigation.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Sarel, Ayelet", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Finkelstein, Arseny", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Las, Liora", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ulanovsky, Nachum", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/e52229261e01a9a400a9faad8d7c3287", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/b50549cdc662e61732f78ccc89f0b5709dd6a7edd6688822a317b501cfc51286", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/DK5RX46U", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/DK5RX46U", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/5168e4c4c697a040413df7f041a2f12b!/b311213-313675", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "6321", "pages": "176-180", "title": "Science", "volume": "355"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/e52229261e01a9a400a9faad8d7c3287"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:DK5RX46U"}, {"identifier": "10.1126